║ SYSTEM ║
║ m Open Tactical Dashboard with live system stats ║
║ h Display this command reference ║
║ up Run 15-step system maintenance ║
║ sysinfo One-line summary: CPU, RAM, disk, GPU ║
║ get-ip Show WSL and WAN IP addresses ║
║ cls Clear screen ║
║ reload Full profile reload ║
║ cpwd Copy working directory to Windows clipboard ║
║ cl Deep cleanup (apt, brew, journal, docker, npm) ║
║ cl --light Light cleanup (python cache only) ║
║ cl --report Show cleanup report (no deletion) ║
║ logtrim Trim logs over 1MB to last 1000 lines ║
║ oedit Open tactical-console.bashrc in VS Code ║
║ code <path> Open any file or directory in VS Code ║
║ pwsh PowerShell 7 (Linux native; shared profile via OneDrive sym║
║ link) ║
